          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "带我与主同到死地，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "知道同钉的奇道。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "从今不再是我工作，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我想，我爱，或我说；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "惟独乃是基督生活，"
